Author: Rodderman
Title: [ANN] Unofficial [KASH]KashCoin currency for the music industry[DJ Lethal]
Body: I found this on the web it looks interesting, not my project, could not find this in the forums.   Why Kashcoin?  Highly Innovative and Simple.  Kashcoin will be accepted at many places across the globe – from music festivals to retail stores.  Giving discounts and perks back to the Kashcoin community.   DJ Lethal and Justin Lally have launched an altcoin for the music industry called Kashcoin. Users will be eligible for deals and perks. The goal is to introduce music lovers to cryptocurrency.  Video! https://youtu.be/OTPlvTpC0GY  Website: https://kashcoin.net/  Steemit: https://steemit.com/bitcoin/@steveo/kashcoin-promises-to-be-the-crypto-currency-for-the-music-industry  Twitter: https://twitter.com/kashcoin  Trade: https://www.cryptopia.co.nz/Exchange/?market=KASH_BTC   specifications for the coin:  – Algo x11  – Premining  – Proofs: Network-Stake (PoS) – Anonymous Burn Destroy (PoBA)  – Min Stake Time of 1 hour, Max Stake Time of 8 hours  – PoW ended at Block 100.000, Mined 1,200,000 KASH  – Minimum Transaction Fee: 0.01 KORE  – RPC Port: 28555, P2Port: 28556  – Confirmations: 10, Maturity: 30
